OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Andrew Tye to Ruturaj Gaikwad, WICKET Ruturaj Gaikwad run out Ravi Bishnoi (Chennai Super Kings 28 Runs for 1 wicket). OverHistory.Commentry: Andrew Tye bowling to MS Dhoni, full length ball, pitching outside off stump, MS Dhoni slices over point for 4 runs
OverHistory.UPDCommentry: Andrew Tye to MS Dhoni, 4 run(s), full length, wide outside off stump, Dhoni frees his arms and slices this over short third man to end the innings with a boundary, and that's 7000 T20 runs for Dhoni. CSK put on 210 on the board after 20 overs. Stay tuned for the chase!
Dhoni finishes the innings with a boundary to reach the milestone of 7000 T20 runs, and Chennai Super Kings score the joint-highest total this season. Can they defend it like how Rajasthan did?
